{sov: V4}
Did he doubt or did he try? Answers aplenty in the bye and bye,
Talk about your plenty, talk about your ills, One man gathers what another man spills.
{eov}

{sot: Lead}
||: No Chords | Drums :|| : E / / / :|| : E / A / :|| E / Dsus2 / |A / E / :||
